--   Add enumeration values to unisEponUniVlanType
--   Add unisEponUniPortIsolate, unisEponUniVlanConfiguration
--   unisEponUniAutoNegotiation, unisEponUniRestartAutoNeg,
--   unisEponUniLinkStatus, unisEponUniInterfaceType
--   to unisEponUniSysManTable.
--   Add unisEponUniPortPolicyTable, unisEponUniMulticastTable.
--   Add unisEponUniMulticastControlTable, unisEponUniQosConfIndexNextTable,
--   unisEponUniQosConfTable, unisEponUniQosRuleTable.
-- V1.4 Updated by liuhongxu,andapeng 2007-10-13
--   Add unisEponUniMulticastFastleave to unisEponUniMulticastTable
--   Add unisEponUniMulticastIndex to unisEponUniMulticastControlTable
--   Add unisEponUniVitualCableTest to unisEponUniSysManTable
--   Add unisEponUniMirrorGroupTable, unisEponUniMirrorGroupIdNextTable
--   Add unisEponUniMulticastCtrlInfoTable
