--   unisEponUniPortPolicyInboundExtraBurst,unisEponUniPortPolicyOutboundCir
--   to unisEponUniPortPolicyTable.
--   Add unisEponUniMulticastIndexNextTable
--   Modify unisEponUniInterfaceType
-- V1.5 Updated by maguoqiang,wangke,zhaodan 2008-1-14
