--      unisEponUniDuplex, unisEponUniVlanVPNStatus, unisEponUniPortIsolate,
--      unisEponUniAutoNegotiation, unisEponUniVitualCableTest
--   Add unisEponUniMulticastSourceIpList to unisEponUniMulticastControlTable
--   Add unisEponUniMulticastResetInterval to unisEponUniMulticastControlTable
--   Modify unisEponUniVCTCableStatus and add 9 nodes:
--   Add    unisEponUniVCTCableLength
--          unisEponUniVCTImpedanceMismatch
--          unisEponUniVCTPairSkew
--          unisEponUniVCTPairSwap
--          unisEponUniVCTPolaritySwap
--          unisEponUniVCTInsertionLoss
--          unisEponUniVCTReturnLoss
--          unisEponUniVCTNearendCrosstalk to unisEponUniSysManTable
